<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Семейное дерево</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://d3js.org/d3.v7.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-tree"></i> Семейное дерево</h1>
            <div class="header-controls">
                <button id="add-person" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Добавить человека
                </button>
                <button id="edit-person" class="btn btn-secondary">
                    <i class="fas fa-edit"></i> Редактировать
                </button>
                <button id="delete-person" class="btn btn-danger">
                    <i class="fas fa-trash"></i> Удалить
                </button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="main-layout">
            <aside class="sidebar">
                <div class="search-container">
                    <input type="text" id="search" placeholder="Поиск по имени или фамилии...">
                    <div id="search-results" class="search-results"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="stats-container">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i> Статистика</h3>
                    <div class="stats-grid">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                            <span>Всего людей:</span>
                            <span id="person-count">0</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-male"></i>
                            <span>Мужчин:</span>
                            <span id="male-count">0</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-female"></i>
                            <span>Женщин:</span>
                            <span id="female-count">0</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i>
                            <span>Поколений:</span>
                            <span id="generation-count">0</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="sidebar-controls">
                    <button id="import-data" class="btn btn-outline">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-import"></i> Импорт
                    </button>
                    <button id="export-data" class="btn btn-outline">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-export"></i> Экспорт
                    </button>
                    <button id="reset-data" class="btn btn-outline">
                        <i class="fas fa-redo"></i> Сброс
                    </button>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <main class="content">
                <div id="tree" class="tree-container"></div>
                <div id="notification" class="notification"></div>
            </main>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Модальные окна -->
    <div id="person-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h2 id="form-title">Добавить человека</h2>
                <span class="close">&times;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <form id="person-form">
                    <input type="hidden" id="person-id">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="name">Имя *</label>
                            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="surname">Фамилия *</label>
                            <input type="text" id="surname" name="surname" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="gender">Пол</label>
                            <select id="gender" name="gender">
                                <option value="M">Мужской</option>
                                <option value="F">Женский</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="birth-date">Дата рождения</label>
                            <input type="date" id="birth-date" name="birth-date">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="death-date">Дата смерти</label>
                            <input type="date" id="death-date" name="death-date">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="father-id">Отец (ID)</label>
                            <input type="text" id="father-id" name="father-id" placeholder="ID отца">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="mother-id">Мать (ID)</label>
                            <input type="text" id="mother-id" name="mother-id" placeholder="ID матери">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-actions">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Сохранить</button>
                        <button type="button" id="cancel-form" class="btn btn-secondary">Отмена</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="delete-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h2>Подтверждение удаления</h2>
                <span class="close">&times;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>Вы уверены, что хотите удалить <strong id="delete-person-name"></strong>?</p>
                <p class="text-warning"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Это действие нельзя отменить!</p>
                <div class="form-actions">
                    <button id="confirm-delete" class="btn btn-danger">Удалить</button>
                    <button id="cancel-delete" class="btn btn-secondary">Отмена</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
